{
  "stem": "9503.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was 12 at that time and not very impressed nor very knowledgeable about sex or anything like that, about sexual issues.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Russians had bicycles, and they had candy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember that I wanted to ride a bike.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I hadn't ridden a bike for I don't know how long, you know, since the Germans took it away in Holland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so there were a-- a bunch of Russians sitting in a park, and they had bicycles on the lawn.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I went up to them, and I pointed to the bike.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he pointed at the grass next to him, and I pointed at the bike.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was like, OK, you can take it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I rode this bike through the camp, pleased as punch.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of my orphanage-- what do you call them-- sleep mates wanted a ride.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, no, I got this from a Russian, and I wouldn't let anybody on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I brought it back, and we, again, had this thing of I should sit down, and I said, uh-uh.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went back, and it was past my regular hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And lo and behold, my mother is there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she asked some of the kids where I was, and they said, with a Russian, or she understood, with a Russian on a bike.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she must have gone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when-- by the time I came walking in there, I got hit by my mother, and that is the only time that I remember being hit by my mother.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She-- she slapped me because she was so worried.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there I was, and I had done something that everybody was told never to do.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
